{"type":"message","id":"189375a7","parentId":"d3db03f4","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:04:26.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经读了 agent-browser 的 SKILL.md 并记录了 learning。现在我需要用正确的工具来帮用户完成这个任务：\n\n1. 打开 B 站\n2. 搜索张雪峰\n3. 找到最热的视频并打开\n4. 找到评论框\n5. 输入\"一路走好！\"并提交\n\n让我开始用 agent-browser 来完成这个任务。\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好，学乖了。🦊 现在用正确的工具帮你完成这个任务。\n\n让我用 `agent-browser` 来操作 B 站：打开网站 → 搜索张雪峰 → 找到最热视频 → 在评论区留言\"一路走好！\"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_95ba7d5d2dc54b27a035ace9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"agent-browser open \"https://www.bilibili.com\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":191,"cacheRead":18100,"cacheWrite":3000,"totalTokens":21297,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00005348,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00005414}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774609460063,"responseId":"msg_4f2442e0-4566-4816-804c-7fecbc723795"}}
